{
  "id": "adv_event_2510_01_02",
  "title": "長瀬さん\nと\n琴乃ちゃん",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――一方、星見高等学校にて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.299999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、次の化学は移動教室だったはずだけど……\nん、長瀬さん……？　えー……あっ、私のこと！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.199999996,
      "endTime": 15.8087301214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.0002035737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "に、二階の実験室なんですね、あ、いえ、なのね……\nあ、ありがとう、桝井さん……助かりました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.0002035737,
      "endTime": 25.3069822907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――放課後、帰り道にて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1984557469,
      "endTime": 27.3984560012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 27.4651224136
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～……『長瀬さん』って……\n前は『琴乃ちゃん』って呼んでくれていたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.2651226639,
      "endTime": 37.2817879319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 37.4732613842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、渚。私ってそんなに話しかけ辛いというか\n……気難しい感じに見えるのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4732613842,
      "endTime": 45.0026286404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 45.1941020926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "ううん。そんなことないよ。でも、突然呼ばれ方が\n変わったりしたら、気にしちゃうよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.1941020926,
      "endTime": 53.5692983588,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 53.7607718111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "そうなの……前はもっと親しかったというか……\nこんな距離感は感じなかったのに……って見てたの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7607718111,
      "endTime": 63.033331171700006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 61.4666655223
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 63.1128819746
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんね！　化学のノートを忘れたのに気が付いて\n教室まで戻った時に、ちょっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.1128819746,
      "endTime": 70.5197335524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 70.712885535
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "そう……確かに最近忙しくて学校に行けてなかったし\n顔を合わせたのは久しぶりだったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.712885535,
      "endTime": 79.6714386584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 79.8629121107
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "なんだかクラスの人達が私に対してちょっとよそよそ\nしい感じがしているの……気にし過ぎなのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8629121107,
      "endTime": 88.6438643736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 88.8353378258
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "久々で距離感が分からなくなっちゃってるのかも\nふふっ、でも、琴乃ちゃん変わったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.8353378258,
      "endTime": 97.34867286309999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.5353393517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "デビューしたての時は学校よりもお仕事優先！\n学校のことなんて全然気にしない、って感じだったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.5353393517,
      "endTime": 104.9384386978,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 105.135332231
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんと{user}さんの話を聞いて\n思ったの。学生生活も大切なんだなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.135332231,
      "endTime": 111.22131865450001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 111.4127921067
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "それから学校のことも意識してみたら\n前よりも少しずつ友達が増えてきた……気がしてて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.4127921067,
      "endTime": 118.69999783829999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "なのに『琴乃ちゃん』から『長瀬さん』呼びに\n戻っちゃうなんて……はあ、どうすればいいのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0036732318,
      "endTime": 130.1309752109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 130.3224486632
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、すぐに解決しないかもだけどもっと琴乃ちゃん\nから積極的にみんなと関わってみるのはどうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3224486632,
      "endTime": 140.15766404099998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 140.3557819965
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "学校行事に参加してみたり、下の名前で呼んでみたり！\n仲良くしたいって思ってるのはみんなも同じだと思うな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.3557819965,
      "endTime": 148.89999885560002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 149.2557728412
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、渚の言う通りかもしれないわね\nもしかして渚が委員会に所属し続けているのも……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.2557728412,
      "endTime": 157.2557759884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 157.4472494407
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　お仕事とかで学校に行ける日は少ないけど\nその分充実した学生生活を送りたいんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.4472494407,
      "endTime": 165.33333218890002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 165.613906952
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだよね。高校生活は今しかないんだもん\nよし、私も頑張ってみる！　ありがとう、渚！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.613906952,
      "endTime": 174.46111764539998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日、ホームルームにて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.3859251979,
      "endTime": 176.78593842220002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.8526050888
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2510_01_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "こ、今回の学園祭実行委員ですが……\nわ、私にやらせていただけないでしょうか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.7192709886,
      "endTime": 184.91834554300002,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-03.m4a",
          "delay": 15680.727867000001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-03.m4a",
          "delay": 15480.727867000012
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.5666655223
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
